      "name": "Battle Song",
      "type": "ability",
      "system": {
        "description": "<p>As long as there are at least 4 of these demons in the same zone, they are able to harmonize their song, creating a tone that melts the glue that holds the tunnels together, causing the zone to collapse, as long as it is in the colony. All 4 must use this action in the same round. The collapse happens at the end of the turn of the final demon.</p>",
